{"id":18808,"date":"2024-01-30T21:50:18","date_gmt":"2021-01-30T16:20:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=18808"},"modified":"2023-05-18T11:43:05","modified_gmt":"2023-05-18T06:13:05","slug":"wardrobe-decoration-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/wardrobe-decoration-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"9 Creative Wardrobe Decor Ideas For Your Bedroom"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Give your wardrobe the much-needed aesthetic facelift with some creative wardrobe decoration ideas. Have a quick look at our latest collection and get inspired to do the makeover<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Well-decorated wardrobes have the potential to become the focal point of attraction in a bedroom, be it the kid\u2019s room, master bedroom or your own private one. It is also a static fixture as compared to the other pieces of furniture and decor in the space which can be replaced\/changed once you feel bored with their looks. Finally, wardrobes can also increase the resale value of your property once you have decided to shift out, owing to the amount of storage space that\u2019s available. The more it is, the merrier it is for potential home buyers!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How Do You Go About Designing Your Dream Bedroom Wardrobe?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Designing a bedroom wardrobe is not as easy as it sounds, though it can be taken up as a wardrobe decoration DIY project as well. You need to consider a number of factors before taking the final step. To spare you the hassle, we\u2019ve prepared a quick checklist for you to read and keep handy so that you choose the right wardrobe for yourself.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><strong>Type of wardrobe:<\/strong> Built-in wardrobe (fixed feature) or a free-standing wardrobe (movable feature) that does not block any source of light in the bedroom<\/li><li><strong>Size of wardrobe:<\/strong> The size of the wardrobe depends upon the amount of storage space you want for your clothes and accessories and the way you want to keep them. Different stuff in your bedroom wardrobe requires different heights to be neatly accommodated, so check the amount of floor space and wall space available. For starters, the ideal wardrobe height for children can be 15 inches while it can be 45 inches for an adult. Check out more <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/wardrobe-interior-design-ideas\/\">wardrobe interior design ideas here<\/a>.&nbsp;<\/li><li><strong>Style of the wardrobe and wardrobe door: <\/strong>The style and colour of the bedroom wardrobe should complement the interiors of the bedroom and other pieces of decor. It shouldn\u2019t dull down the overall vibe of the room. If you\u2019re looking for modern wardrobe decoration, you can also experiment with sliding doors instead of swing or hinge ones as they\u2019re quite a trend these days. Here too, you will need to measure the space around the wardrobe to ensure that there\u2019s enough for free movement around the room. Skim through more <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/wardrobe-door-design-ideas\/\">wardrobe door design ideas here<\/a>.<\/li><li>There are a few more pointers to keep in mind, so check them out right <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/how-to-choose-wardrobe-for-bedroom\/\">here<\/a>.&nbsp;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>How to decorate your wardrobe? Here are nine creative ideas you can try.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wardrobe Decoration That Is A Piece Of Art<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This navy blue and white check-patterned wardrobe is a piece of art and will surely win compliments from your friends and visitors. You can get this look by either using two different kinds of laminates or creatively using pieces of self-adhesive and easy-to-remove wallpaper on the wardrobe doors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214208\/check-patterned-wardrobe-decoration.jpg\" alt=\"Navy blue and white check patterned wardrobe decoration in the bedroom.\" class=\"wp-image-18810\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214208\/check-patterned-wardrobe-decoration.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214208\/check-patterned-wardrobe-decoration-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214208\/check-patterned-wardrobe-decoration-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214208\/check-patterned-wardrobe-decoration-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>This wardrobe lends a cool and stylish vibe to the bedroom space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Animate The Doors For A Quintessential Wardrobe Decoration<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This is one of the easiest ways of doing DIY wardrobe decoration for your little girl\u2019s bedroom. Instantly bring life to the wardrobe doors, that too without spending much, by using animated stickers or painting them.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214214\/decorate-wardrobe-doors-with-animation.jpg\" alt=\"White and pink coloured wardrobe door decorated with animated stickers in the kids' bedroom, wardrobe decoration DIY.\" class=\"wp-image-18811\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214214\/decorate-wardrobe-doors-with-animation.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214214\/decorate-wardrobe-doors-with-animation-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214214\/decorate-wardrobe-doors-with-animation-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214214\/decorate-wardrobe-doors-with-animation-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>This butterfly wardrobe decor creates visual drama in the bedroom and evokes your child\u2019s creative imagination<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Novel Wardrobe Decoration Ideas: Door Knobs Can Also Make A Statement<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Find funky door knobs\/handles for your plain white wardrobe to blend it with the overall theme of the bedroom. It adds a pop of bright colour and a fun ambience to the room without being too bold or overwhelming.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214301\/wardrobe-decoration-idea-with-funky-door-knobs.jpg\" alt=\"White wardrobe door knobs decorated in yellow house shape is how to decorate the wardrobe in kid bedroom.\" class=\"wp-image-18819\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214301\/wardrobe-decoration-idea-with-funky-door-knobs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214301\/wardrobe-decoration-idea-with-funky-door-knobs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214301\/wardrobe-decoration-idea-with-funky-door-knobs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214301\/wardrobe-decoration-idea-with-funky-door-knobs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The yellow door handles are in complete sync and symmetry with the room\u2019s wallpaper and decor<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Experiment With Decorative Laminates<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Incorporate interesting patterns on your wardrobe using decorative laminates instead of the solid colours.&nbsp;Laminates are also a popular alternative to the typical wooden wardrobes doors and are currently trending. In this context, check out some <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wardrobe-laminate-design\/\">laminate wardrobe design ideas here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214220\/decorative-laminates-for-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom wardrobe door decorated in beige floral patterns is decorative laminate for wardrobe.\" class=\"wp-image-18812\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214220\/decorative-laminates-for-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214220\/decorative-laminates-for-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214220\/decorative-laminates-for-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214220\/decorative-laminates-for-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>This floral beige laminate wardrobe looks elegant and sophisticated in this bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mirror Mirror On The Wall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This wardrobe decoration with crystal clear decorative mirror panels visually maximises the bedroom space and oozes opulence and sophistication. The panels also reflect the light, hence making the room look brighter and airier.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214244\/mirror-door-wardrobe-decoration-idea.jpg\" alt=\"Wardrobe decoration idea, wardrobe doors decorated with crystal clear mirror panels look airy in the blue bedroom.\" class=\"wp-image-18816\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214244\/mirror-door-wardrobe-decoration-idea.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214244\/mirror-door-wardrobe-decoration-idea-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214244\/mirror-door-wardrobe-decoration-idea-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214244\/mirror-door-wardrobe-decoration-idea-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The room\u2019s blue walls, lightwood flooring along with the mirrors transport you to a tropical beach<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Now I\u2019m There&#8230;Now I\u2019m Not<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Opt for a separate \u2018his and her\u2019 wardrobe to maximise the space and configure the storage of items according to your individual needs and lifestyle. Use patterned\/etched glass to beautify the doors and create some visual symmetry in the bedroom space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214249\/patterned-mirror-door-wardrobe-decoration.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom decorated wardrobe doors with patterned glass look gorgeous.\" class=\"wp-image-18817\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214249\/patterned-mirror-door-wardrobe-decoration.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214249\/patterned-mirror-door-wardrobe-decoration-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214249\/patterned-mirror-door-wardrobe-decoration-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214249\/patterned-mirror-door-wardrobe-decoration-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>These patterned mirror doors give you much-needed privacy<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Slide Away<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This black and silver sliding door wardrobe looks bold and moody and also lends a luxurious ambience to the bedroom. Sliding doors are a boon for small bedrooms as they don\u2019t take up much floor space and can be easily handled on a day-to-day basis. Check out more <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sliding-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">sliding wardrobe design ideas<\/a> here.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214225\/home-decor-sliding-wardrobe-doors.jpg\" alt=\"Home decor sliding wardrobe doors in black and silver lamination looks bold in the white bedroom.\" class=\"wp-image-18813\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214225\/home-decor-sliding-wardrobe-doors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214225\/home-decor-sliding-wardrobe-doors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214225\/home-decor-sliding-wardrobe-doors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214225\/home-decor-sliding-wardrobe-doors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Sliding wardrobe doors look modern and are great space-savers as well<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Eyeing modular wardrobes for your smart home?\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/09124436\/eyeing-modular-wardrobes-for-your-smart-home.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Trims Offer A Neater Look<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Architectural wooden trims on standard wardrobe doors allow for a beautiful combination of textures and patterns. They instantly accentuate the wardrobe\u2019s exteriors and also mimic the royal look and match the room\u2019s interiors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214231\/home-decor-wardrobe-door-with-wooden-trims.jpg\" alt=\"Wardrobe decoration idea, Lavender-coloured wardrobe door decorated in textures and patterns looks royal in the bedroom.\" class=\"wp-image-18814\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214231\/home-decor-wardrobe-door-with-wooden-trims.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214231\/home-decor-wardrobe-door-with-wooden-trims-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214231\/home-decor-wardrobe-door-with-wooden-trims-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214231\/home-decor-wardrobe-door-with-wooden-trims-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The trims on this lavender-coloured wardrobe give it a completely new and fresh look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wardrobes Can Have Secrets Too<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Add extra storage spaces for all those items that are small and not very frequently used in unconventional places in your wardrobe, like this secret side compartment. You can even add a mirror on the inside so that it makes for a space-saving dressing area as well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214238\/how-to-decorate-wardrobe-with-secret-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Home decor wardrobe, Grey coloured wardrobe designed with a secret side compartment in the bedroom.\" class=\"wp-image-18815\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214238\/how-to-decorate-wardrobe-with-secret-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214238\/how-to-decorate-wardrobe-with-secret-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214238\/how-to-decorate-wardrobe-with-secret-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/30214238\/how-to-decorate-wardrobe-with-secret-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The grey wardrobe is a perfect fit in this bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Decorating your bedroom wardrobe can actually give you an opportunity to give a personal touch to your bedroom and transform it into a style statement. Give us a call or email us if you want more guidance for your wardrobe decoration project. Good luck!<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row d